================= clscMath Test Program =================

-- Positivity Check --
5 is positive? 1
-3 is negative? 1
0 is zero? 1

-- Odd / Even --
7 is odd? 1
10 is even? 1

-- Prime Check --
7 is prime? 1
12 is prime? 0

-- Palindrome Check --
121 is palindrome? 1
123 is palindrome? 0

-- Perfect Number Check --
6 is perfect? 1
10 is perfect? 0

-- Reverse Number --
Reverse of 1234: 4321

-- Sum of Digits --
Sum of digits of 1234: 10

-- Number to Text --
1234 in words: One Thousands Two Hundreds Thirty Four

-- Basic Math Operations --
Sum(5, 10, 15) = 30
Subtract(50, 10, 5) = 35
Multiplicate(2, 3, 4) = 24
Divide(100, 2, 5) = 2
Mode2Num(17, 5) = 2

-- Utility Functions --
ABS(-12) = 12
Opposite(12) = -12
Half(25) = 12.5

-- Ceil / Floor / Round --
Ceil(5.2) = 6
Floor(5.9) = 5
Round(5.5) = 6
Round(-5.5) = -6

-- Random Number (1-10) --
4 9 2 7 10 

================= End of Tests =================

